{"tid":1225893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社引述資深警官　不滿林鄭處理手法　形容為瘋狂","createTime":"2019-06-15T08:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T11:13:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":934,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"0b80f59d593a913e22a0c85e46d790c5ea6ae66c","tid":1225893,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"立法會原訂於周三 （12日）就修訂逃犯條例恢復二讀，惹起大批市民包圍立法會，最終引發警民衝突，警方更出動橡膠子彈和布袋彈驅散，超過80人受傷。路透社周五（14日）報道，引述多名資深警官指，衝突事件令他們感到左右兩難，又認為示威者要求撤回修例的訴求並非不合理，一切源於港人對內地法律制度的不信任。<br />\n<br />\n報道續引述，林鄭月娥漠視民意經已引起警隊不滿，指責她處理今次危機手法，形容為「瘋狂」（Madness）。而今次能夠解決問題的並非警隊或示威者，唯獨是林鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n而另一資深執法人員表示，今次示威者比以往更加堅定，倘政府不讓步，暴力將持續升級。"},{"pid":"3bc473c4bb8da7888826018fd5730eda9ca59b38","tid":1225893,"uid":237562,"like":338,"dislike":3,"score":335,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:56:33.000Z","msg":"互割<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66dae624271bb52e871244447ce18aff379216ec","tid":1225893,"uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:56:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/340950/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E8%AD%A6%E5%AE%98-%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E6%89%8B%E6%B3%95-%E5%BD%A2%E5%AE%B9%E7%82%BA%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F340950%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%2598%258B%25E7%258B%2