br />\n<br />\n大家都係專心聽日遊行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"Reuters: <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/mobile.reuters.com/article/amp/idUSKCN1TF1BU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fmobile.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Famp%2FidUSKCN1TF1BU&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJda0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=aee50a98\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/mobile.reuters.com/article/amp/idUSKCN1TF1BU</a>"},{"pid":"fd8e4a0ef1f4bedc582c067fe81d63ef42c0807b","tid":1225893,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafb9e36527c5438c0db6cea9db9c7ebd79e4351","tid":1225893,"uid":37396,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>立法會原訂於周三 （12日）就修訂逃犯條例恢復二讀，惹起大批市民包圍立法會，最終引發警民衝突，警方更出動橡膠子彈和布袋彈驅散，超過80人受傷。路透社周五（14日）報道，引述多名資深警官指，衝突事件令他們感到左右兩難，又認為示威者要求撤回修例的訴求並非不合理，一切源於港人對內地法律制度的不信任。<br />\n<br />\n報道續引述，林鄭月娥漠視民意經已引起警隊不滿，指責她處理今次危機手法，形容為「瘋狂」（Madness）。而今次能夠解決問題的並非警隊或示威者，唯獨是林鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而另一資深執法人員表示，今次示威者比以往更加堅定，倘政府不讓步，暴力將持續升級</span>。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句點出咗今次行動點解比以前有效<br />\n同埋由和理非開始逐步升級成勇武嘅重要性"},{"pid":"cd98c8f078eeddc30100478b48e7cd7d09117584","tid":1225893,"uid":83602,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"癲得過你班狗?<br />\n咪諗住割呀"},{"pid":"893194a6a75d63d794b11459aa47b4ee74dc6d15","tid":1225893,"uid":5289,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:05:59.000Z","msg":"做得警隊都唔會有良心<br />\n<br />\n冇良心既都走曬"},{"pid":"491e0fec9e02f7fbe72fcbfd0f81b5b761bc0680","tid":1225893,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:06:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做得警隊都唔會有良心<br />\n<br />\n有良心既都走曬</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4ca5c3d11a478d5daeb53ad0b719bfef54403647","tid":1225893,"uid":18639,"like"