一切源於港人對內地法律制度的不信任。<br />\n<br />\n報道續引述，林鄭月娥漠視民意經已引起警隊不滿，指責她處理今次危機手法，形容為「瘋狂」（Madness）。而今次能夠解決問題的並非警隊或示威者，唯獨是林鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n而另一資深執法人員表示，今次示威者比以往更加堅定，倘政府不讓步，暴力將持續升級。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:34:06.000Z","msg":"心理戰見效了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢連一哥都擺上台，更何況下面果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c44341655c259f0a83d9d9e0a1be9bfd9c6394c","tid":1225893,"uid":103346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:34:28.000Z","msg":"最後一句<br />\n<br />\n示威者只更加堅定<br />\n因為知道咁做係有效<br />\n下次只會更加激烈"},{"pid":"5bbbcf86bb8918f9e43318743fbc77b5013500f2","tid":1225893,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:34:37.000Z","msg":"現場指揮官判斷黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e32996b06a301bbc0d4ed37abe7055ccf919be4","tid":1225893,"uid":259302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:34:45.000Z","msg":"1.撤回修例<br />\n2.收回示威是暴動的定性<br />\n3.釋放所有過去一週因示威被捕的人<br />\n4.追究警方使用過份武力，甚至暴力<br />\n若明天和平遊行有人叫「林鄭下台」「打倒中共」「港獨」等無關上述四點的口號，請勿理會，現在要集中目標。"},{"pid":"8ae2efe4b119fc3087269657e1f7edc5a893b87e","tid":1225893,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:36:12.000Z","msg":"咁又落order開槍"},{"pid":"7700d64b2608a89beee382a395ac3a75e80a64a2","tid":1225893,"uid":56299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:38:19.000Z","msg":"被全世界割蓆都無離棄過班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a474d19cb47134dec2d8f20